        <h1 class="study-title">2 Kings 19</h1>
        <p class="study-subtitle">Word-by-Word Hebrew-English Interlinear</p>
      </header>
      
      <div class="chapter-nav">
        <span><a href="2ki-18.html">&larr; Chapter 18</a></span>
